Comment: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:26.23,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna and the Hot Spring Ping Pong
Comment: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was about to go straight to Heaven!
Comment: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Comment: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to sleep farther away from you.
Comment: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, you have to chain me to a pillar or...
Comment: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chaining yourself up?\NThat's an admirable attitude.
Comment: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Want me to chain you up right now?\NFuyuzora Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna! Kogarashi! Morning!
Comment: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Comment: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morning.
Comment: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna, I'm really sorry about yesterday.
Comment: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I took a relaxing bath, oblivious that\Nyou were placed in serious danger.
Comment: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about it.
Comment: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After all, I asked you to pretend I wasn't here.
Comment: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I didn't want to scare the new tenant,\Nso I was going to hide as much as possible.
Comment: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But you weren't hidden at all.
Comment: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,At any rate, I was surprised to find out\Nthat you're a psychic.
Comment: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm the one who was surprised.\NI didn't know all of you can see Yuuna.
Comment: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No wonder you can live here\Nwithout being bothered by it.
Comment: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you're all ghosts.
Comment: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm very much alive. See?
Comment: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here, take a good look.
Comment: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have legs.
Comment: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Comment: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're being indecent, Nonko!
Comment: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have legs, too!
Comment: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't have to show me!
Comment: 0,0:03:58.19,0:04:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But the longer a ghost has been dead, the harder\Nit is to differentiate them from a living human.
Comment: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then do you want to verify it?
Comment: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,See? I'm soft.
Comment: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And you can hear it, right?
Comment: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The beating of my heart...
Comment: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right?
Comment: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing?
Comment: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi, you're being so bashful\Nand it's so adorable.
Comment: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You smell like booze!
Comment: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You start drinking in the morning?
Comment: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's more unusual when Nonko isn't drinking.
Comment: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You bastard! Again!
Comment: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is it my fault?
Comment: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay\Nsharing a room with a man like this?
Comment: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can not only see Yuuna,\Nbut you can also touch her.
Comment: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Has he done anything strange to you?
Comment: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Anything strange?
Comment: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-N-N-No, nothing at all!
Comment: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Something definitely happened!
Comment: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-H-How dare you, Fuyuzora Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was all unavoidable!
Comment: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There's a hollow tree in the hill behind us.
Comment: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}GRRRR
Comment: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's perfect for a beast like you!
Comment: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please, at least treat him like a human!
Comment: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not sleeping in a place\Nwhere I'd drown if it rains!
Comment: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Have you had that experience?
Comment: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have no intention of moving out.\NThe room I'm renting is Room 4.
Comment: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Besides, I promised Yuuna\Nthat I'd ascend her to Heaven.
Comment: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It is something she'll have to do eventually.
Comment: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And I don't want to see Yuuna falling to Hell.
Comment: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know.
Comment: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning, Kogarashi and Yuuna.
Comment: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Comment: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll serve some breakfast at once.
Comment: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Comment: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Comment: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can wait for you to pay for your meals\Nup to one month.
Comment: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,One day later than that\Nand you get nothing to eat.
Comment: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right.
Comment: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She may be short, but she's also formidable.
Comment: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, sure.\NShe's the oldest one here at Yuragi Inn.
Comment: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What? So she's just older than she looks.
Comment: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya, did you sleep under the table again?
Comment: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morning.
Comment: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Were you under there the whole time?
Comment: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, ears?
Comment: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A tail?
Comment: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya, your tail!
Comment: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We can see your panties, too!
Comment: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Try to cover up, at least!
Comment: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't get tired of this, huh?
Comment: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi is a psychic,\Nso there's no reason to hide it.
Comment: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,At least hide your panties, idiot!
Comment: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Breakfast is ready!
Comment: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong, everyone?
Comment: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You people...
Comment: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you?
Comment: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's right.
Comment: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why don't we take this opportunity\Nto re-introduce ourselves?
Comment: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,First, I'm...
Comment: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Comment: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's the guy from yesterday...
Comment: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now you've done it this time, whelp!
Comment: 0,0:07:57.18,0:08:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If I look carefully with my spirit vision,\Nit's a nest of man-eating fiends!
Comment: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We, the Gudon Clan, will exterminate all of you!
Comment: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But Master Sekkan,\Nthey've all taken on the form of women.
Comment: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And they look unexpectedly lovely.
Comment: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know if we should\Nhandle them in a rough manner.
Comment: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Enough!
Comment: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We will annihilate the demons\Nand the human who sides with them!
Comment: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then instead, capture the women and use them\Nhowever you like for your training!
Comment: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Use them...
Comment: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,however we like?
Comment: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No...
Comment: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see! That would be like saving them, too!
Comment: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's what I was thinking, too!
Comment: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Me too!
Comment: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Those morons.
Comment: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry, this is my fault.
Comment: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Everyone, please hide inside.
Comment: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, you should get back.
Comment: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ameno School Demon-slaying Technique!
Comment: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Secret technique!
Comment: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Autumn Shower!
Comment: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What the...
Comment: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Since Sagiri is a demon-slaying ninja,\Nher spirit weapons
Comment: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,appear and disappear,\Nas well as change their appearance!
Comment: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What is a demon-slaying ninja?
Comment: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't falter! Charge!
Comment: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your heads are all so smooth, just like balls!
Comment: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, can I play some bowling?
Comment: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B-Bowling?
Comment: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What is this super strength?
Comment: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Look! This woman has a horn on her forehead!
Comment: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,An ogre?
Comment: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Comment: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There!
Comment: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Strike!
Comment: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She sent them all flying, dang.
Comment: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The more Nonko drinks, the stronger she gets.\NShe's a descendant of Shuten-douji!
Comment: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Curse you, damn it!\NHow could I have known that it would be...
Comment: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. You can play with them.
Comment: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya is possessed by that adorable cat god!
Comment: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You won't do anything yourself?
Comment: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I'm so sleepy.
Comment: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Comment: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Totally annihilated?
Comment: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, we'll regroup and come back again\Nand then we'll definitely...
Comment: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir? That won't do.
Comment: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wee!
Comment: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's that light?
Comment: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I won first prize in the lottery?
Comment: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I passed the Johnny's Entertainment audition?
Comment: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm the heir of a billionaire's fortune?
Comment: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My 100 million-yen debt has been forgiven?
Comment: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My pooch has come home?
Comment: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I get to participate in a ground-breaking\Nhair growth clinical trial?
Comment: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm done exterminating monsters!
Comment: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is why young monks...
Comment: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad, I'm sorry.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that I've become a parent,\NI've finally realized how wrong I was.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So please, quit being a monk and come home.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay. I will.
Comment: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I won't forget this, demons!
Comment: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I swear I'll pay you back someday!
Comment: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Comment: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Happily ever after!
Comment: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wha...
Comment: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's Ms. Nakai, the caretaker who's been here\Nat Yuragi Inn longer than any of us.
Comment: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's actually a protective household deity\Nwho manipulates luck.
Comment: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's incredible!\NCan you share some luck with me, too?
Comment: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You really shouldn't.
Comment: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That ability uses the luck they already possess.
Comment: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I hope they didn't use\Nall of their lifetime of luck in one shot.
Comment: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Scary!
Comment: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ms. Nakai is the most powerful, after all.
Comment: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, now that we've\Nproperly introduced ourselves...
Comment: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,let's welcome our new tenant with a greeting.
Comment: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Welcome to Yuragi Inn!
Comment: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Kogarashi thought to himself.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}"If I don't be careful,\NI'll end up going to Heaven first before Yuuna."{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, good.\NLooks like I'm not in the sky this morning.
Comment: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wha...
Comment: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}This is bad.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Before Yuuna wakes up,\NI need to get out from here.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi, good morning.
Comment: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- No!\N- Of course!
Comment: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That man did something again?
Comment: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I apologize. Every morning...
Comment: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll be more careful.
Comment: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, please.
Comment: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, how did you get inside?
Comment: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- C'mere! C'mere!\N- Kogarashi, that cat is...
Comment: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}These guys helped me a lot\Nback when I slept outside.
Comment: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}They're so warm.
Comment: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What, you don't like this?
Comment: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Real charmer, huh?
Comment: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even though I'm petting you.
Comment: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ow!
Comment: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're... Yaya?!
Comment: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri.
Comment: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bastard. What's the meaning of this?
Comment: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi was groping me all over my body.
Comment: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even though I hate to be touched.
Comment: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was just petting a cat!
Comment: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Divine punishment!
Comment: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Petition
Comment: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It grieves me to say this, but I received a petition\Nto evict Fuyuzora Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And so, in order to resolve this issue speedily,\Nin accordance with Yuragi boarding house rules,
Comment: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,we're going to hold a one-game match.
Comment: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yay!
Comment: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Boarding house rules?
Comment: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ironclad rules established\Nby the current innkeeper.
Comment: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You'll get terrible amounts of bad luck\Nif you disobey them.
Comment: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Comment: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The loser has to do\Nwhat the winner wishes. Okay?
Comment: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course.
Comment: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I guess I have no choice.
Comment: 0,0:15:57.12,0:16:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The competition is a traditional one\Nhere at Yuragi Inn.
Comment: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- That's right!\N- Hot springs ping pong!
Comment: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Doubles one-game match!
Comment: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's do our best, Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right. I can't stand ping pong.
Comment: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're already making excuses for your loss?
Comment: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How pathetic.
Comment: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, I've never really played ping pong before.
Comment: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm hazy on the rules, too.
Comment: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I think you can play however you want to.\NI don't think they'll play by the rules anyway.
Comment: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There it is! Yaya's paw serve!
Comment: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Use the racket!
Comment: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's hard to tell where the ball will go, right?
Comment: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So will Kogarashi\Nbe able to return this irregular serve?!
Comment: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wha...
Comment: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:16:57.47,0:17:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi hit it back beautifully.
Comment: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That was great, Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So your claim to hate ping pong was a lie!
Comment: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It wasn't a lie.
Comment: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A long time ago\NI was possessed by a ping pong coach.
Comment: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because of all the tough training that I didn't\Neven want to do, I've come to hate ping pong.
Comment: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Although thanks to that, I got good enough\Nto play at national tournaments.
Comment: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then I'll get serious, too.
Comment: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Whoa! Sagiri's specialty,\NClone Creation Technique.
Comment: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that allowed?
Comment: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,One point for Sagiri and Yaya Team!
Comment: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't even hit those!
Comment: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just hold on, Yuuna!\NSoon I'll set you free from that immoral man!
Comment: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, Kogarashi isn't immoral!
Comment: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He isn't immoral...
Comment: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He isn't like that!
Comment: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,One point for Kogarashi and Yuuna Team!
Comment: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good job!
Comment: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice one, Yuuna!\NKeep that up for the next one too!
Comment: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Poltergeist.
Comment: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why is she defending a guy like that?
Comment: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apparently my poltergeist ability activates\Nwhen I remember something embarrassing.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Whoa, Yuuna is hitting\Na series of magnificent returns!
Comment: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri and Yaya are hanging on,\Nbut it looks like they're on the ropes!
Comment: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is the match all but decided?
Comment: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,At last, it's the match point\Nfor Kogarashi and Yuuna Team!
Comment: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For Yuuna's sake,\NI won't let you have your way!
Comment: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Yuuna!\N- Yes!
Comment: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The poltergeist...
Comment: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,didn't happen.
Comment: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna?
Comment: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How could this be?
Comment: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It seems like I've gotten used to\Nremembering embarrassing things!
Comment: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Wha...\N- Hold on, Yuuna.
Comment: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll free you from that man at once!
Comment: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Whoa! They've caught up!\NThis is an exciting development!
Comment: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do? At this rate, Kogarashi will...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it's come to this, then I must...\NBut I can't...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's all over!
Comment: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just obediently leave Yuragi Inn!
Comment: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I promised to make Yuuna happy!
Comment: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't afford to leave now!
Comment: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll at least give you credit\Nfor that chivalrous spirit.
Comment: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But this is the end!
Comment: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please... look...
Comment: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri's ball is out!
Comment: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Game set!
Comment: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The winner is Kogarashi and Yuuna Team!
Comment: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Comment: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna, that's enough! We won!
Comment: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's thanks to you!
Comment: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,O-O-On second thought, please don't look!
Comment: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So we've won the challenge, right?
Comment: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. A loss is a loss.
Comment: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It pains me to say this, but I promise\NI won't try to kick you out anymore.
Comment: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But remember this.
Comment: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you do anything to harm us, getting\Nthrown out would be the least of your worries.
Comment: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do anything like that. Sheesh.
Comment: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's heavy, isn't it? I'll help, too.
Comment: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That was my bad.
Comment: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi, hang in there!
Comment: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:21:57.48,0:22:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kogarashi was anxious about relations\Nwith the other tenants in the days to come.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next time: Yuuna Goes to School
Comment: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't miss the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:02.00,YamiSora,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&\3c&H408DE1&\3a&HFF&}............... {\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H408DE1&\3a&H00&}YAMISORA FANSUB\NBiên dịch: Tuyền Oa Minh Nhân
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì đây...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Này, Yuuna! Làm cái gì...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ủa, Kogarashi-san, chào buổi sáng...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu, đây là, trên trời?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình hay lăn qua lăn lại trong khi ngủ ấy mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lăn đi xa quá rồi đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chúc ngủ ngon...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rớt bây giờ...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:26.54,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Yuuna và Bóng bàn Suối nước nóng
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tí nữa là lên chơi với Ngọc Đế luôn rồi đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Cho mình xin lỗi mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lần sau mình sẽ nằm ngủ xa cậu hơn mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không, chắc phải trói tớ vào cái cột hay là...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tự trói mình ư?\NTa có lời khen đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có cần ta trói ngay bây giờ luôn không, Fuyuzora Kogarashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna-chan! Kogarashi-chan! Chào buổi sáng~!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chào buổi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chào.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna, chuyện hôm qua tớ rất xin lỗi cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tớ chỉ mãi lo tắm mà không biết rằng cậu đang gặp nguy hiểm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Biết làm sao được chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dù gì mình cũng nhờ mọi người cứ vờ như mình không có ở đây mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình không muốn làm khách trọ mới chuyển tới sợ, nên mới tính trốn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng cuối cùng có trốn được đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cơ mà, không ngờ nhà ngươi lại là linh lực giả đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tui mới là người ngạc nhiên đấy, không ngờ ở đây ai cũng nhìn thấy Yuuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hèn chi mấy người có thể sống như không có gì xảy ra như thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đừng nói mấy người cũng là ma đấy nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chị vẫn còn sống nhăn răng đấy, này!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nè, nhìn kỹ đi nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có chân luôn nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đúng thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bất lịch sự quá đấy, Nonko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình cũng có chân nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ai cần cậu show ra hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:04:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng nếu vong linh tồn tại càng lâu thì càng khó phân biệt với người sống.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy cậu có muốn xác nhận không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nè, mềm chưa này.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu nghe thấy mà phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Từng nhịp đập con tim chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Này! Chị làm cái gì thế?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-chan ngượng rồi, dễ thương chưa kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Người nồng nặc mùi rượu nữa chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chị uống rượu từ sáng giờ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hiếm khi thấy Nonko-san không uống rượu lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tên khốn! Người dám làm thế nữa à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Là lỗi của tui à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ở chung phòng với tên này có ổn không thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không chỉ thấy được Yuuna, mà còn chạm được vào cậu ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tên này có làm chuyện gì lạ lùng với cậu không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lạ lùng à...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,K-K-Không có gì đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế này thì chắc chắn là có rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,T-T-Tên khốn kiếp, Fuyuzora Kogarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Toàn mấy chuyện bất khả kháng mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sau nhà trọ có một cái cây rỗng ruột.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chỗ đó hợp với loài thú vật như ngươi đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ít nhất hãy coi cậu ấy là người đi chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không có chuyện tui ngủ ở cái nơi mưa ngập mặt lần nữa đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu trải qua chuyện đó rồi à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tui không định chuyển đi đâu, phòng trọ của tôi là phòng số 4 mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hơn nữa, tui đã hứa sẽ giúp Yuuna siêu thoát.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đến một lúc nào đấy, chuyện đó sẽ xảy đến nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chị không muốn thấy cảnh Yuuna-chan bị đày xuống địa ngục đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em hiểu mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A, chào buổi sáng Kogarashi-kun, Yuuna-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chào buổi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chị đi chuẩn bị bữa sáng nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tiền ăn phải trả trong vòng 1 tháng nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trễ một ngày là xác định cạp đất thay cơm nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhỏ người vậy mà đáng sợ thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thì đúng là vậy mà, chị ấy là người lớn tuổi nhất nhà trọ Yuragi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hể? Ra là dáng học sinh tuổi phụ huynh à.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya-san, cậu lại ngủ dưới gầm bàn nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chào buổi sáng~!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ở dưới đó suốt luôn à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cơ mà, tai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đuôi nữa chứ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya-san, đuôi cậu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lộ cả quần lót luôn kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Che lại dùm cái!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora Kogarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mãi éo thấy chán à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi là linh lực giả mà, nên không cần giấu chúng đi cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chí ít cũng che quần lót lại chứ, đồ ngốc này.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đã để mọi người đợi lâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chuyện gì thế mấy đứa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mấy cô...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,là cái giống gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải rồi ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hiếm khi có dịp, nên nhân đây chúng ta tự giới thiệu luôn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trước tiên, chị là...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ra đây mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Là tên hôm qua!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cuối cùng cũng chịu ló mặt ra, tiểu tử!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:08:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Linh thị của ta mách rằng, chỗ đó là động yêu ma ăn thịt người!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì cơ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tộc Gudan bọn ta sẽ xoá sổ hết các ngươi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng mà Sekkan-dono, bọn chúng đều mang hình hài phụ nữ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lại còn toàn là mỹ nhân nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nên em không biết có nên xử chúng theo cách thô bạo không...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cắt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ác ma hay con người, miễn đứng về phe bọn chúng là diệt hết!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy thì, bắt mấy ả đó rồi dùng chúng để luyện tập ra sao thì tuỳ ý các ngươi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gi cơ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dùng chúng...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,tuỳ thích...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không~!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hiểu rồi! Thế thì nhanh nhanh cứu họ thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bần tăng cũng nghĩ vậy đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bần tăng nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bọn ngốc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi, là lỗi của tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mọi người, vào trong trốn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngươi nên lùi lại đi thì hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trừ yêu Nhẫn pháp phái Ameno!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bí kỹ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tùng Thời Vũ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì thế...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri-san là nhẫn giả trừ yêu, nên linh khí của cậu ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,có thể xuất nhập, biến hoán tuỳ ý!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhẫn giả trừ yêu là cái giống gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Còn đứng đó à! Xông lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đầu của mọi người láng như quả bóng ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nè nè, cho tui mượn chơi bowling tí nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B-Bowling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sức mạnh thần thánh gì thế này?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhìn kìa! Trên trán ả này có sừng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Là quỷ à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đến đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bay nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bay mất dạng hết rồi kìa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:09.98,Sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}酒呑童子 (Shutendouji) - Tửu thôn Đồng tử (Cậu bé Nghiện rượu) là con quỷ thống lĩnh quỷ tộc trong thần thoại Nhật Bản
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Càng uống nhiều rượu thì Nonko-san càng mạnh, hậu duệ của Tửu thôn Đồng tử mà lỵ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Khốn kiếp! Nếu biết trước xảy ra chuyện thế này...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ừm, quẩy nhiệt tình vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya-san thì có một Miêu Thần cực kỳ dễ thương theo bên mình đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Còn cô thì chả làm gì hết à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thì Yaya buồn ngủ mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không thể nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gục hết rồi ư?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không, phải tập hợp lại, để lần sau quay lại còn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi quý khách, như thế là hổng được đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lên nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ánh sáng đó là?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trúng số độc đắc ư?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đỗ kỳ thử giọng của Johnny Audition rồi ư?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Được làm người thừa kế của tỉ phú ư?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Khoản nợ 100 triệu Yên được xoá rồi ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Con cún về rồi ư?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình được tham gia buổi thử nghiệm thuốc mọc tóc siêu tốc ư?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trừ yêu diệt quái cái beep, dẹp hết đê!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì cơ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cái lũ hoà thượng non dạ này...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.33,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Ba, con xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:53.75,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Trở thành bậc cha mẹ rồi con mới nhận ra mình đã sai ở đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:57.38,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nên là, ba đừng xuất gia nữa, về nhà với con đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ừ, ba hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhớ mặt bọn bây đấy, lũ yêu ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thù này nhất định ta sẽ trả!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin cảm ơn~!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chúc mọi người hạnh phúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Người ở nhà trọ Yuragi lâu nhất, và cũng là chủ trọ, chính là Nakai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chị ấy là gia thần có khả năng điều khiển vận hạnh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ghê thiệt, vậy chia cho tớ ít vận may nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bỏ ý nghĩ đó đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bọn chúng chỉ đang dùng vận may của chính mình thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chỉ mong là họ không dùng hết vận may cả đời trong 1 lần thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đáng sợ thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quả nhiên Nakai-san là bá đạo nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy, ai cũng đã tự giới thiệu cả rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,giờ thì ta cùng chào mừng khách trọ mới nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chào mừng đến với nhà trọ Yuragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mong được giúp đỡ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:03.78,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi đã nghĩ rằng...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:10.83,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,"Mình mà bất cẩn là thăng trước cả Yuuna luôn", vậy đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ơn trời, xem ra sáng ngay không phải nằm giữa trời xanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.07,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Bỏ mợ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:44.03,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Trước khi Yuuna dậy, mình phải ra khỏi đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san, chào buổi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Không!\N- Biết ngay mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tên đó, lại gây ra chuyện gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi cậu vì sáng nào cũng gây ra chuyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lần sau mình sẽ chú ý hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ừ, nhờ cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sao mày vào đây được thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san, bé mèo đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hồi còn ngủ ngoài đường, bọn mày giúp tao nhiều lắm đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ấm ghê luôn chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì thế, mày không thích à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đáng yêu vậy cơ mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Được tao vuốt ve mà còn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đau!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mày là... Yaya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora Kogarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tên khốn, thế này là sao hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi sờ soạng khắp cơ thể Yaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya ghé bị sờ soạng, vậy mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tui chỉ vuốt ve con mèo thôi mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thiên Tru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.58,Sign,NTP,0,0,0,,ĐƠN YÊU CẦU
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dù rất buồn, nhưng chị đã nhận được 1 đơn yêu cầu đuổi Fuyuzora Kogarashi-san ra khỏi đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Và, để giải quyết ổn thoả chuyện này, chiếu theo nguyên tắc ở trọ ở nhà trọ Yuragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,chúng ta sẽ tổ chức một trận so tài.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nguyên tắc ở trọ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đó là nguyên tắc thép do chủ trọ hiện tại đưa ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu dám chống lại thì xác định bị vận xui ập xuống đầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thiệt hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bên nào thua thì phải nghe theo lời bên thắng nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dĩ nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cũng đâu còn cách nào khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:16:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So tài là một phong tục truyền thống ở nhà trọ Yuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Đúng thế!\N- Bóng bàn suối nước nóng!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đấu cặp ăn thua trong 1 trận!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cùng cố gắng nào, Kogarashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ừ, mình ngán tận cổ cái trò bóng bàn này rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chưa đánh đã đầu hàng sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thảm hại thật đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À, trước giờ mình chưa chơi bóng bàn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nên vẫn chưa rõ luật.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mà, muốn chơi sao cũng được, tớ nghĩ họ cũng không nắm rõ luật đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đến rồi! Pha giao bóng bằng tay của tuyển thủ Yaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dùng cái vợt dùm cái!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Khó có thể đoán được bóng sẽ bay tới chỗ nào nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Giờ thì, tuyển thủ Kogarashi có đáp trả được pha giao bóng ảo diệu này không đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì cơ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:17:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cú phản công rất đẹp từ tuyển thủ Kogarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tuyệt ghê, Kogarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhà ngươi, vậy ra ngươi nói không thích bóng bàn là xạo à!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không phải xạo đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hồi xưa tui từng bị vong của thằng cha huấn luyện viên bóng bàn ám.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bị bắt luyện tập như trâu như ngựa dù bản thân không muốn, thế là ghét luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mà cũng nhờ đó mà trình của tui mạnh ngang mấy tay chơi cấp quốc gia đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy thì ta cũng chơi nghiêm túc!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ô! Tuyệt kỹ của tuyển thủ Sagiri, phân thân chi thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trò đó mà cũng được phép dùng à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 điểm cho đội Sagiri-san và Yaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.18,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế này thì đánh bằng niềm tin chắc!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chờ nhé Yuuna, tớ sẽ sớm giải thoát cậu khỏi tên vô đạo đức đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Làm gì có, Kogarashi-san đâu có vô đạo đức!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không có vô đạo đức...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu ấy không phải người như thế!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 điểm cho đội Kogarashi-kun và Yuuna-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Khá lắm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice, Yuuna! Giữ phong độ như thế ở mấy cú tiếp theo nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Poltergeist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sao lại vì một tên như thế mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:29.69,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Xem ra khi mình nhớ phải chuyện gì xấu hổ thì sẽ thi triển được poltergeist nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ô, tuyển thủ Yuuna liên tục phản công!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tuyển thủ Sagiri và Yaya đang đỡ bóng, nhưng xem ra họ đang rất khổ sở.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không lẽ kết quả đã được định rồi sao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cuối cùng, 1 điểm nữa thôi là đội của tuyển thủ Kogarashi và Yuuna sẽ giành chiến thắng!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vì Yuuna, ta sẽ không để ngươi làm càn đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Yuuna!\N- Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Poltergeist...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,không kích hoạt...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sao lại thế này chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hình như mình đã quen với việc nhớ mấy chuyện xấu hổ mất rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chờ tớ, Yuuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tớ sẽ giải thoát cậu khỏi tên đó ngay đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ô, tỉ số đã san bằng, quả là bước tiến không ngờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:34.09,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Tính sao giờ, cứ thế này thì Kogarashi-san sẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:38.30,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Đã vậy thì, nhưng, chuyện như thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kết thúc rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngoan ngoãn cút khỏi nhà trọ Yuragi đi là vừa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình đã hứa sẽ đem đến hạnh phúc cho Yuuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nên sẽ không có chuyện mình bị đuổi đi đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ta có lời khen tinh thần trượng nghĩa của ngươi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng đến đây là kết thúc rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhìn... mình này...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cú phát bóng của Sagiri-san ra ngoài rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Game set!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đội Kogarashi-kuns và Yuuna-san giành chiến thắng!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sao có thể?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna, đủ rồi, chúng ta thắng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhờ cậu cả đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đ-Đ-Đúng là... đừng có nhìn mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy, bọn tui thắng rồi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ờ, thua là thua.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dù không muốn nói ra, nhưng ta hứa sẽ không cố đuổi ngươi ra khỏi đây nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng nhớ đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu ngươi mà dám động đến một cọng lông của bọn ta thì cứ chuẩn bị tinh thần đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Làm gì có chuyện đó chứ, thiệt tình.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cái đó nặng lắm phải không, để tui giúp một ta...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vừa rồi là lỗi của tui...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora Kogarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san, gắng lên...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:22:04.53,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Từ giờ hẳn Kogarashi sẽ rất lo về mối quan hệ với những người ở trọ khác đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:40.00,Next Episode,NTP,0,0,0,,YUUNA ĐI HỌC
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhớ đón xem tập tuần sau nhé.
